Package: opengl-pm
Version: 0.54
Revision: 1
Depends: x11, glut-shlibs
BuildDepends: x11, glut
Source: mirror:cpan:authors/id/I/IL/ILYAZ/modules/OpenGL-0.54.tar.gz
Source-MD5: ff53886f6fc0d81ddde0e40725c8e33b
SourceDirectory: OpenGL-%v
PatchScript: sed -e 's,@PREFIX@,%p,g' %a/%f.patch | patch -p1
Type: perl
UpdatePOD: true
DocFiles: COPYRIGHT INSTALL MANIFEST README* SUPPORTS TODO
CompileScript: <<
  perl Makefile.PL PREFIX=%p INSTALLPRIVLIB=%p/lib/perl5 INSTALLARCHLIB=%p/lib/perl5/darwin INSTALLSITELIB=%p/lib/perl5 INSTALLSITEARCH=%p/lib/perl5/darwin INSTALLMAN1DIR=%p/share/man/man1 INSTALLMAN3DIR=%p/share/man/man3
  make LDDLFLAGS="-bundle -L/System/Library/Perl/darwin/CORE -lperl -L/usr/X11R6/lib -lGL -L/sw/lib -lglut"
<<
InstallScript: <<
  mkdir -p %i/share/doc/%n
  cp -Rp examples %i/share/doc/%n/examples
  make install INSTALLPRIVLIB=%d%p/lib/perl5 INSTALLARCHLIB=%d%p/lib/perl5/darwin INSTALLSITELIB=%d%p/lib/perl5 INSTALLSITEARCH=%d%p/lib/perl5/darwin INSTALLMAN1DIR=%d%p/share/man/man1 INSTALLMAN3DIR=%d%p/share/man/man3
<<
Description: Perl module for working with OpenGL
DescDetail: <<
This module provides access to most of the OpenGL 1.0, 1.1, and 1.2 APIs.
Some amount of GLU is supported (I'm not quite sure what version it works
out to), and GLUT should be completely supported up to API version 3. A
small portion of GLX and X11 is supported, as an alternative to GLUT.
<<
